The much-anticipated testimony of former Eskom CFO, Anoj Singh has been postponed. His legal team requested that it rescheduled. Singh was due to appear at the State Capture Commission of Inquiry this morning. Barry Bateman has more. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The anticipated testimony of former Eskom CFO, Anoj Singh has been postponed. Singh's lawyer has told the commission that he is not yet in a position to give evidence. READ: Saica expels Anoj Singh This because of a misunderstanding about non-existent affidavits from evidence leader, Pule Seleka. Singh was due to appear at the state capture inquiry on Wednesday morning.